description: Exports the specified notebook and its metadata.

parameters.name: NotebookId
parameters.description: The ID of the notebook to export.

nested_items.name: NotebookMetadata
nested_items.description: The notebook metadata, including notebook ID, notebook name, and workgroup name.

nested_items.name: WorkGroup
nested_items.description: The name of the Spark enabled workgroup to which the notebook belongs.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The time when the notebook was created.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: The type of notebook. Currently, the only valid type is IPYNB.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The time when the notebook was last modified.

nested_items.name: Payload
nested_items.description: The content of the exported notebook.
